title: Nevada Election Results Could Take Days, Officials Say
description: Overwhelmed state election officials say that they have been flooded by thousands of mail-in ballots, many of which will not be counted until Thursday.
dc:creator: Julie Brown
media:credit: Mikayla Whitmore for The New York Times
media:description: Senator Catherine Cortez Masto, left, and Gov. Steve Sisolak at a Nevada Democratic election night party in Las Vegas on Tuesday.
